\id 1JN  - Dobu NT [dob] -Papua New Guinea 1985 (web version -2013) 
\h 1 YONI 
\toc1 Yoni ꞌIna ꞌEtoladi ꞌEbweuna 
\toc2 1 Yoni 
\toc3 1 Yo 
\mt1 YONI ꞌINA ꞌETOLADI ꞌEBWEUNA  
\mt2 Yoni ꞌina leta gete solanaya ꞌiemwasala oboboma be maedana be yawasi ataya Yesu ꞌenega manudi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Ona nina yawasida manuna  
\p
\v 1-2 \x * \xo 1:1-2 \xt Yo 1:1-2, 4\x*\x * \xo 1:1-2 \xt Yo 1:14\x*Gimi tutaya ona nina yawasida manuna Tamada maꞌiyana simiyami, ꞌenega ꞌaboꞌama wate tenamega ꞌanonona, ta wate nimamega tai nina ꞌagitoona, manuna niꞌatu ꞌiapwesama ta matamega ꞌaꞌitena, ga tauna manuna ꞌasimasimana ꞌemiya, nate tauna yawasi ataya ꞌalena, ta lowa tauna Tamana maꞌiyana simiyamiya, niꞌatu ꞌiapwesama ꞌemaya.   
\p
\v 3 Tauna ꞌaꞌitena ta ꞌanonona ga ꞌemiya ꞌasimanena be ꞌaene ꞌomi maꞌemao taegosigosiyana leleleya, ta wate Tamada be Natuna Yesu Keliso maꞌedao taegosigosiyana leleleya.  
\v 4 ꞌEnega ꞌimi leta gete niꞌatu ꞌaꞌetoladinawa, be ꞌenega wada sawa, be wada gwausowala ꞌaiꞌaila.   
\s1 Yaubada maedana ꞌalena  
\p
\v 5 \x * \xo 1:5 \xt 1 Ti 6:16; Ye 1:17\x*ꞌEnega tetela gete ꞌieonema, ga ꞌasimanena ꞌemiya ꞌaene Yaubada maedana ꞌalena, ta nigeya wate ꞌebweu guguyoi ꞌenaya ꞌimiyami.  
\v 6 \x * \xo 1:6 \xt 1 Yo 2:4\x*ꞌEnega ꞌabo sena guguyoi ꞌenaya tamiyami, geyaꞌabo takabokabo be tagwae ꞌaene, “Yaubada maꞌedai taegosiyana.” Nate nigeya bubuna palupaluna.  
\v 7 Ta ꞌeguma sena maedana ꞌena tamiyami, nadigega Yaubada nina sena maedana ꞌena ꞌimiyami, nate taegosigosiyana ꞌaiꞌaila, manuna Natuna Yesu lalanega ꞌigieꞌesaseda ꞌida toꞌumalinao maiboꞌadi ꞌediyega.   
\p
\v 8 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, maiboꞌada totoꞌumalida tuga, ta geyaꞌabo takabokaboeda, be tagwae, “ꞌAboꞌagu boboꞌagu, ta nigeya ꞌigu toꞌumalinamo.”  
\v 9 Ta esi ꞌeguma tasimana ꞌaiꞌaili be tagwae, “O! Niꞌatu yaloegesi,” Yaubada ꞌida toꞌumalinao ꞌida nuwataudi be ꞌenega ꞌigieꞌesasa ꞌaiꞌailida, sawesawenaya be Yaubada tauna Topalupaluna taemise.   
\p
\v 10 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌeguma tagwae, “Nigeya wate ꞌebweu tuta yaloeloegesi,” nate Yaubada taꞌawaꞌawa kabokaboe, manuna ꞌina ona nigeya taemiemise.   
\c 2  
\s1 Keliso tauna ꞌada tolema  
\p
\v 1 \x * \xo 2:1 \xt Ib 9:24\x*Ye natugwao, ꞌimi leta gete yaꞌetoladinawa be ꞌenega geyaꞌabo waguiguinuwa gesi. Ta ꞌeguma taloegesi, Yesu Keliso tauna topalupaluna ꞌisisida manuda, Tamana ꞌenaya,  
\v 2 \x * \xo 2:2 \xt Lo 3:25; Yo 1:29, 11:52\x*be ꞌida toꞌumalinao ꞌinuwataudi, manuna Yesu tauna ꞌitaliyaena ꞌida toꞌumalinao manudi, be wate me baleꞌu maiboꞌadi manudi.   
\p
\v 3 Yaubada nina tamwalatonina ꞌaene gosiya ꞌaiꞌailida, ꞌeguma ꞌina loinao taematamatanedi.  
\v 4 \x * \xo 2:4 \xt 1 Yo 1:6, 8\x*ꞌEnega ꞌeguma yaita ꞌionaona be ꞌigwae, “ꞌAboꞌagu Yaubada gosiyagu,” ta Yaubada ꞌina loinao nigeya ꞌida ematamatanedi, nate ꞌikabokabo, manuna ꞌeda palupaluna ꞌipilisinena.  
\v 5 \x * \xo 2:5 \xt Yo 14:21, 23; 1 Yo 4:12, 17, 5:3\x*Ta ꞌabo Yaubada ꞌina ona tamulimuliye, ꞌina oboboma ꞌenega ꞌiloemaeda be tamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene gosedai nina maꞌeda tamiyami.  
\v 6 \x * \xo 2:6 \xt Yo 13:15\x*ꞌEnega ꞌeguma yaita ꞌoyo ꞌugwae, “ꞌAboꞌagu Yaubada gosiyagu ta maꞌiyagu ꞌamiyami,” ꞌilobwene ꞌaiꞌailiyo be ꞌuda bubuna nadigega Yesu ꞌina bubuna.   
\s1 Loina auwauna  
\p
\v 7 \x * \xo 2:7 \xt 2 Yo 5-6\x*Gosegwao, geyaꞌabo loina auwauna yaꞌetoꞌetoladinawa, ta esi loina kadekadelina nina wagimi nononaya, ga niꞌatu wamwalatonina, gete yalolimenawa.   
\p
\v 8 \x * \xo 2:8 \xt Yo 1:9; Lo 13:12\x*Ta esi loina gete yaꞌetoladi limena ꞌatuwa loina auwauna, oboboma manuna, manuna oboboma nina Keliso ꞌana lobwene, ta ꞌomi ꞌami lobwene wate. Nate ꞌenega guguyoi ꞌisawasawala, ta maedana ꞌaiꞌaila niꞌatu ꞌisaema.   
\p
\v 9 \x * \xo 2:9 \xt 1 Yo 3:10, 15, 4:20\x*ꞌEnega ꞌeguma yaita tasina ꞌietalauwale be ꞌionaona ꞌaene tauna maedana ꞌena ꞌimiyami, nate ꞌikabokabo, manuna tauna ꞌetamo tuga guguyoi ꞌena ꞌimiyami.  
\v 10 \x * \xo 2:10 \xt Lo 14:13\x*Ta wate ꞌabo yaita ꞌoyo gosemwao ꞌuobobomedi, ꞌoyo maedana ꞌena ꞌumiyami, ꞌenega geyaꞌabo ꞌubeꞌubeꞌu.  
\v 11 \x * \xo 2:11 \xt Yo 12:35\x*Ta esi ꞌabo tasiyo ꞌuetalauwale, ꞌalena gete manuna ꞌoyo ꞌetamo guguyoi ꞌina sena ꞌena ꞌumiyami, ta wate guguyoi ꞌena ꞌutautauya, be ꞌeda geyaꞌabo ꞌuꞌitaꞌita, manuna matayo guguyoi ꞌiumabodena.   
\p
\v 12 \x * \xo 2:12 \xt 1 Ko 6:11\x*Gogama ye, ona gete yaꞌetoladinawa manuna ꞌimi loegesiyao Yaubada ꞌinuwataudi, Yesu ꞌana esanega.   
\p
\v 13 ꞌEnaꞌiyao ye, ona gete yaꞌetoladinawa manuna ꞌomi tauna lowaenei ga batuwa ꞌimiyami niꞌatu wamwalamwalatoni.  
\p Tubuwauyao ye, ona gete yaꞌetoladinawa, manuna tauna totoꞌumalina sana niꞌatu waewaiwai sinena.  
\p Ta ꞌomi gogama sinasinabwami ona gete yaꞌetoladinawa, manuna Tamada niꞌatu wamwalatonina.   
\p
\v 14 ꞌEnaꞌiyao ye, ona gete yaꞌetoladinawa manuna ꞌomi tauna lowaenei ga batuwa ꞌimiyami niꞌatu wamwalamwalatoni.  
\p Tubuwauyao ye, ona gete yaꞌetoladinawa, manuna ꞌomi toewaiwai sami ga Yaubada ꞌina ona ꞌimiyami ꞌemiya, ꞌenega tauna totoꞌumalina sana niꞌatu waewaiwai sinena.   
\p
\v 15 \x * \xo 2:15 \xt Lo 8:7; Ye 4:4\x*Gosegwao, geyaꞌabo baleꞌu gete nuwami ꞌiꞌewaꞌewa, manuna ꞌeguma baleꞌu gwegwenao nuwami ꞌiꞌewai, gete ꞌenega Tamadai wanuwa pupule, ta nigeya wada obobomena.   
\p
\v 16 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, baleꞌu yagenao maiboꞌana, nate yalakwaiya be gwegwe ꞌana yala be nuwatuꞌe, yage getedi nigeya Tamada ꞌenega simeemai, ta esi baleꞌu ꞌenega.  
\v 17 \x * \xo 2:17 \xt Md 7:21\x*Ta baleꞌu gete ꞌiabe ꞌisasawala ta wate nuwanuwa gwegwe baleꞌu manuna ꞌigugumwala, ta ꞌaboꞌada esi ꞌeguma Yaubada ꞌina nuwanuwa taguiguinuwe tamiya ataya.   
\s1 Keliso ꞌana talauwala nina  
\p
\v 18 \x * \xo 2:18 \xt Md 24:5, 24; 2 Yo 7\x*Natugwao, tuta ꞌana ꞌebe losalowa niꞌatu ꞌimai saba, ta lowa wanonona ꞌaene Keliso ꞌana talauwala nina ꞌiabe ꞌiapwesama, ꞌenega wada nuwaꞌiꞌisi Keliso ꞌana talauwalao yaudi baleꞌuya simiyami, ꞌenega tamwalamwalatoni tuta ꞌana ꞌebe losalowa gete,  
\v 19 \x * \xo 2:19 \xt Gu 20:30\x*ta Keliso ꞌana talauwalao nidi ꞌadi ꞌita ꞌatuwa Keliso ꞌana toemisao, ta nigeya. Manuna taudi ꞌeguma ꞌida boda ꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌetamo maꞌedao tamiyami. Ta nigeya saꞌi! Niꞌatu sipilisineda.   
\p
\v 20 Ta ꞌomi taudi nigeya nadigega, manuna niꞌatu Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌigiesinapumi, ga ꞌenega mwalatoi yauna wasinapudi,  
\v 21 ta nigeya ꞌaene ma imi emwagemwage ꞌimi leta gete wasawasawai, manuna eꞌita palupaluna niꞌatu wamwalatonina, ta wate wasinapuna ꞌaene nigeya wate ꞌebweu kabo ꞌiapweapwesama bubuna palupaluna ꞌenega.   
\p
\v 22 \x * \xo 2:22 \xt Md 10:32-33; 1 Yo 4:3; 2 Yo 7\x*Ta taudi tokabo nidi Yesu sieyaseyaseye, ta sigwae, “Yesu tauna nigeya Toꞌetoseyana.” ꞌAbo yaisigedi sionaona nadigega, taudi Keliso ꞌana talauwalao, manuna Keliso maTamana siguitoyasedi.   
\p
\v 23 \x * \xo 2:23 \xt Md 10:32-33; Yo 5:23; 2 Yo 9\x*ꞌEnega ꞌeguma yaita ꞌoyo Yaubada Natuna ꞌuguitoyasena, nigeya Yaubada maꞌiyayo wamiyami. Ta esi ꞌeguma ꞌutagwaleyo Natuna ꞌenaya, tauna be Tamana maꞌemwao wamiyami.   
\p
\v 24 ꞌOmi lowa tetelidi wanonona, ꞌenega ꞌabo tetela nina ꞌemiya ꞌimiyami tauna be Tamana maꞌemiyao wamiyami,  
\v 25 \x * \xo 2:25 \xt Yo 3:15, 6:40\x*be yawasida nina ꞌiona upaupaenaya ꞌida ꞌebwaꞌemi, nate yawasi ataya.   
\p
\v 26 Gete maiboꞌana niꞌatu yaꞌetoladinawa be ꞌaene wada sinapu taudi ꞌami tokaboyao manudi.  
\v 27 \x * \xo 2:27 \xt Yo 14:26\x*Ta mwalatoi nina niꞌatu wamwalatonina, manuna Yaubada Yaluyaluwana niꞌatu ꞌiꞌebwaꞌemi, ga maꞌemi wamiyami, ta ꞌieꞌitemi. ꞌEnega nigeya ꞌebweu wate tai sawesawenaya be ꞌieꞌitami, ta esi Yaubada ꞌina ꞌebwaya ꞌenega mwalatoi yauna wasinapuna, nate mwalatoi ꞌaiꞌaila manuna. Yaubada Yaluyaluwana nigeya sawesawenaya be ꞌikaboeda. ꞌEnega ꞌina eꞌitao wamuliyedi, be Keliso maꞌemi wamiyami, ta geyaꞌabo wapilipilisine.   
\s1 Yaubada Natunao manudi  
\p
\v 28 \x * \xo 2:28 \xt 1 Yo 4:17\x*ꞌEnega natugwao, ꞌilobwenemi be Keliso ꞌena wamiya ataya, ꞌenega ꞌabo tuta nina ꞌiapwesama, geyaꞌabo ma imi matauta, nai ma imi omayamaya, ta esi wada gwausowala ꞌina mai manuna.   
\p
\v 29 \x * \xo 2:29 \xt 1 Yo 3:10\x*Ta Yaubada wate wada mwalatoni ꞌaene tauna Topalupaluna, ꞌenega ꞌabo yaisigedi taudi siguinuwa palupaluna, taudi Yaubada ꞌenega situbuwama.   
\c 3  
\p
\v 1 \x * \xo 3:1 \xt Yo 1:12-13, 16:3\x*ꞌAboꞌada ꞌeguma Yaubada ꞌenega tatubuwa, tauna ꞌida ꞌawanatuneda. Gete ꞌina oboboma sinabwa wawasae manuda. Onaꞌaiꞌaila, me baleꞌu Yaubada nigeya simwalamwalatoni, ꞌenega me baleꞌu geyaꞌabo siꞌinaꞌinaneda ꞌaene ꞌaboꞌada Yaubada natunao.  
\v 2 \x * \xo 3:2 \xt 2 Ko 3:18; Pi 3:21\x*Gosegwao, gete tuga Yaubada ꞌiꞌawanatuneda be maꞌetamo toꞌase ꞌiapwesa ꞌedaya? Nate namo tamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene ꞌina ilalimanama ꞌenaya ꞌana ꞌita tauna tada ꞌita, ta ꞌaboꞌada ꞌada ꞌita ꞌiesaꞌu gelasedi be tauna nadigega.   
\p
\v 3 ꞌIda emisa yage gete manuna ꞌenega ꞌida bubuna tagieꞌesasedi, nadigega Keliso.   
\p
\v 4 Ta esi totoꞌumalidi Yaubada ꞌina loina sileꞌoaleꞌoa, nate bubuna toꞌumalina.  
\v 5 \x * \xo 3:5 \xt 2 Ko 5:21; 1 Pi 2:22-24\x*Ta wate tamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene Keliso nina ꞌimai ꞌida bubuna toꞌumalidi sabi ꞌewayauledi, ta tauna nigeya ꞌebweu wate ꞌina toꞌumalinamo.  
\v 6 \x * \xo 3:6 \xt Lo 6:1-2, 14\x*ꞌEnega ꞌeguma ꞌaboꞌada Keliso maꞌedai tamiyami geyaꞌabo wate tabuubuna toꞌumalina, ta esi taudi totoꞌumalidi nigeya Keliso siꞌitaꞌita, ta wate nigeya simwalamwalatoni.   
\p
\v 7 \x * \xo 3:7 \xt 1 Yo 2:29\x*Natugwao, geyaꞌabo eꞌita kabokabo wamulimuliye, ta esi nuwami sida sabwalena ꞌaene ꞌabo yaisigedi taudi ꞌidi bubuna boboꞌana, taudi nate toboboꞌadi, nadigega Keliso.  
\v 8 \x * \xo 3:8 \xt Yo 8:44\x*Ta totoꞌumalidi nate taudi Seitani ꞌina bodao, manuna gimituta ꞌenega ga batuwa Seitani tauna totoꞌumalina. ꞌEnega Yaubada Natuna ꞌietunena ga baleꞌuya ꞌimai Seitani ꞌina guinuwao sabi ꞌausepaledi.  
\v 9 \x * \xo 3:9 \xt 1 Yo 5:18\x*ꞌEnega wate ꞌeguma Yaubada ꞌenega tatubuwama geyaꞌabo taguiguinuwa toꞌumalina, manuna bubuna auwauna ꞌatedaya niꞌatu ꞌisaꞌuna, ꞌenega ꞌaboꞌada Yaubada natunao nigeya sawesawenaya be toꞌumalina wate taguinuwe.   
\p
\v 10 ꞌEnega taudi taꞌinanedi ꞌaene yaisigedi Yaubada natunao, ta yaisigedi Seitani ꞌina bodao, manuna taudi Seitani ꞌina boda geyaꞌabo saꞌi siguiguinuwa palupalu, manuna nigeya situbutubuwama Yaubada ꞌenega, ta wate geyaꞌabo sieobooboboma matasidiyao.   
\s1 Oboboma gosedao ꞌediya  
\p
\v 11 \x * \xo 3:11 \xt Yo 13:34-35\x*Emataluwa sinabwana gete ꞌagimi eonemi ꞌaene gosedao maiboꞌadi tada obobomedi.  
\v 12 \x * \xo 3:12 \xt Nug 4:8\x*Ta geyaꞌabo Keni nadigega, manuna Keni nina Seitani ꞌina boda, ga tasina ꞌiununa. Ta ꞌina loemwamasa ꞌalena tuga eꞌipiꞌipi, manuna tasina ꞌina guinuwa boboꞌana ta Keni nina ꞌina guinuwa toꞌumalina.  
\v 13 \x * \xo 3:13 \xt Yo 15:18-19; Md 5:11-12\x*ꞌEnega tasigwao, geyaꞌabo wanuwanuwa owana ꞌabo me baleꞌu sietalauwaleda.  
\v 14 \x * \xo 3:14 \xt 1 Yo 2:11\x*Ta tamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene mwawasa ꞌina sena niꞌatu taebesinena, manuna ꞌatedega gosedao taoboobobomedi, ga yawasida ataya niꞌatu talobena. Ta ꞌeguma yaisigedi taudi nigeya oboboma ꞌatediya, taudi tuga maꞌetamo mwawasa ꞌina sena ꞌena simiyami.  
\v 15 \x * \xo 3:15 \xt Md 5:21-22\x*Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌeguma yaita tasina ꞌietalauwale, tauna toloemwawasa tuga, ta wamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene geyaꞌabo taudi toloemwawasa nidi yawasidi ataya silobaloba.  
\v 16 \x * \xo 3:16 \xt Yo 13:1; 1 Te 2:8\x*Ta wate oboboma tamwalatonina, nate ꞌaene Keliso yawasina ꞌitagwalena ga manuda ꞌimwawasa, ꞌenega ꞌilobweneda wate be yawasida tatagwale tasidao manudi.   
\p
\v 17 \x * \xo 3:17 \xt 2 Loi 15:7; Ye 2:15-16\x*Wada nuwaꞌiꞌisi ꞌaene ꞌeguma yaita toesaesa ꞌimiyami, ta gosiyana ꞌebweu ꞌimiyamwau, be ꞌeguma nigeya ꞌebweu wate lema ꞌiꞌebwaꞌebwaꞌe, mwaꞌadega Yaubada ꞌina oboboma ꞌatenaya? Nigeya.   
\p
\v 18 Natugwao, geyaꞌabo ꞌida oboboma ona namo ꞌenega, ta esi ꞌida guinuwega be tada oboboma ꞌaiꞌaila.   
\s1 Geyaꞌabo tamatamatauta Yaubada matanaya  
\p
\v 19 ꞌEguma ꞌida guinuwega taeobooboboma, gete ꞌena tamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene eꞌita ꞌaiꞌaila ꞌena tamiyami, be geyaꞌabo tamatamatauta Yaubada matanaya.  
\v 20 Ta ꞌeguma ma ida ꞌatesaꞌala ꞌaene ꞌaboꞌada totoꞌumalida, Yaubada ꞌatesaꞌala nidi ꞌida kweudi, manuna yage yauna sawesawenaya, ta wate mwalatoi maiboꞌana ꞌisinapudi.   
\p
\v 21 Gosegwao, ꞌeguma nigeya ꞌida ꞌebe ꞌatesaꞌalamo, kapekapeyana be taꞌatepatu Yaubada matanaya,  
\v 22 \x * \xo 3:22 \xt Md 21:22\x*be ꞌabo toꞌase taside ꞌenaya ꞌida ꞌebwaꞌeda, manuna tauna ꞌina loinao taematamatanedi, ta ꞌida guinuwao manudi ꞌigwausowala.  
\v 23 \x * \xo 3:23 \xt Yo 6:29, 13:34\x*Ta ꞌina loina ꞌeluwa nidi ꞌaene Natuna Yesu Keliso taemise, be gosedao taobobomedi, nadigega Keliso nina ꞌada loina ꞌiꞌebwaꞌeda.   
\p
\v 24 \x * \xo 3:24 \xt Lo 8:9\x*ꞌEnega ꞌeguma ꞌina loinao tamulimuliyedi, ꞌaboꞌada ꞌenaya tamiyami, ta tauna ꞌedaya ꞌimiyami. Ta mwaꞌadega ꞌina miya ꞌedaya tamwalatoiꞌese? Manuna Yaluyaluwana ꞌiꞌebwaꞌeda, ga ꞌedaya ꞌimiyami.   
\c 4  
\s1 Keliso ꞌana talauwala yaluyaluwa toꞌumalidi  
\p
\v 1 \x * \xo 4:1 \xt Md 24:11\x*Gosegwao, geyaꞌabo yaluyaluwa maiboꞌadi waemiemisedi, ta esi watoodi, boboꞌadi nai toꞌumalidi. ꞌEguma taudi boboꞌadi, tamwalatonidi ꞌaene Yaubada ꞌenega simai, ta taudi toꞌumalidi mali senega simai, manuna gete tuga palopita kabokaboyao siapweapwesama mayaluyaluwadi nigeya Yaubada ꞌenega.  
\v 2 \x * \xo 4:2 \xt 1 Ko 12:3\x*Ta esi Yaubada Yaluyaluwana wada mwalatoni ꞌaene ꞌeguma Yesu Keliso taꞌawaꞌaiꞌaile ꞌaene ꞌietomotai baleꞌuya, ꞌida ona nidi nate Yaubada Yaluyaluwana ꞌenega.  
\v 3 \x * \xo 4:3 \xt 2 Yo 7\x*Ta esi yaluyaluwa nidi ꞌabo Yesu sieyaseyaseyena, taudi nigeya Yaubada ꞌenega, ta esi Keliso ꞌana talauwala yaluyaluwana ꞌenega, ta talauwala nina ꞌina mai ꞌalena lowa wanonona, ta onaꞌaiꞌaila, gete tuga bada baleꞌuya ꞌimiyami.   
\p
\v 4 Natugwao, ꞌomi Yaubada ꞌenega watubuwama, ꞌenega mali yaluyaluwa nidi niꞌatu waewaiwai sinedi, manuna Yaluyaluwa nina ꞌedaya ꞌimiyami Toewaiwai sana, ta yaluyaluwa nina me baleꞌu ꞌediya ꞌimiyami ꞌina waiwai nigeya sinabwana.   
\p
\v 5 \x * \xo 4:5 \xt Yo 15:19\x*Ta taudi me baleꞌu bubuna baleꞌu manuna sionaona, ꞌenega me baleꞌu yaudi ꞌenadi sinonona.   
\p
\v 6 \x * \xo 4:6 \xt Yo 8:47\x*Ta ꞌaboꞌada esi Yaubada ꞌenega tatubuwama, ꞌenega ꞌabo yaisigedi taudi Yaubada ꞌana tomwalatoiyao ꞌenada sinonona, ta taudi nigeya Yaubada simwalamwalatoni ꞌenada geyaꞌabo sinonona. ꞌEnega tamwalatonina ꞌaene yaluyaluwa kabokabona ꞌediya ꞌimiyami, manuna ꞌeguma yaluyaluwa ꞌaiꞌaila ꞌediya ꞌimiyami ꞌenada sida nono.   
\s1 Yaubada oboboma ꞌalena  
\p
\v 7 Gosegwao, maiboꞌada tada eoboobobomeda, manuna Yaubada oboboma ꞌalena, ꞌenega toobobomao taudi niꞌatu Yaubada ꞌienatunedi, ta taudi Yaubada ꞌana tomwalatoiyao.  
\v 8 Ta esi taudi nigeya tooboboma, taudi nigeya Yaubada ꞌana tomwalatoiyao, manuna Yaubada oboboma ꞌalena,  
\v 9 \x * \xo 4:9 \xt Yo 3:16\x*ga ꞌina oboboma ꞌigieapwesena ꞌedaya Natuna ꞌenega, manuna Natuna tebweuna nina ꞌietunenama, ga baleꞌuya ꞌimai, be ꞌaene yawasi ꞌaiꞌaila ꞌiꞌebwaꞌeda.   
\p
\v 10 \x * \xo 4:10 \xt Lo 5:8-10\x*Gete oboboma ꞌaiꞌaila, nigeya ꞌaene ꞌaboꞌada Yaubada ꞌana toobobomao, ta Yaubada esi ꞌada tooboboma, ga Natuna ꞌitagwalena be ꞌitaliyaena tauna ꞌida loegesiyao manudi.  
\v 11 \x * \xo 4:11 \xt Md 18:33\x*Gote ꞌena Yaubada ꞌina oboboma ꞌedaya ꞌisinabwa wawasae. ꞌEnega gosegwao, ꞌilobweneda be tauda tada eoboobobomeda.   
\p
\v 12 \x * \xo 4:12 \xt Yo 1:18\x*Nigeya ꞌebweu tuta me baleꞌu Yaubada sida ꞌitena, ta ꞌaboꞌada esi ꞌida eoboobobomega tauda ꞌebweuna ꞌebweuna ꞌenaya nate ꞌenega Yaubada nina maꞌedai, ta wate ꞌina oboboma ꞌaiꞌaila ꞌatedaya ꞌimiyami.  
\v 13 \x * \xo 4:13 \xt 2 Ko 1:21-22\x*Ta wate tamwalatonina ꞌaene ꞌaboꞌada ꞌenaya ta tauna ꞌedaya, manuna yaluyaluwana niꞌatu ꞌiꞌebwaꞌeda.   
\p
\v 14 \x * \xo 4:14 \xt Yo 3:17\x*Ta ꞌaboꞌama matamega Yaubada Natuna ꞌaꞌitena, ga manuna ꞌasimasimana ꞌaene Tamana baleꞌuya ꞌietunenama ꞌaene ꞌada Toꞌetoseyana.   
\p
\v 15 ꞌEnega ꞌeguma yaita ꞌoyo ꞌuꞌawaꞌaiꞌaila ꞌaene Yesu tauna Yaubada Natuna, Yaubada ꞌemuya ꞌimiyami ta yawasiyo tauna ꞌenaya.   
\p
\v 16 \x * \xo 4:16 \xt Yo 6:69\x*ꞌEnega Yaubada ꞌina oboboma ꞌedaya niꞌatu tamwalatonina ga taꞌawa ꞌaiꞌailena.  
\p Onaꞌaiꞌaila, Yaubada oboboma ꞌalena, ꞌenega ꞌabo yaita oboboma ꞌina sena ꞌena ꞌimiyami, tauna Yaubada ꞌena ꞌimiyami, ta Yaubada saꞌi tauna wate ꞌenaya ꞌimiyami.   
\p
\v 17 Gete ꞌenega taeobooboboma ꞌaiꞌaila be bwaꞌomatana ꞌana ꞌasiyata ꞌenaya geyaꞌabo tamatamatauta, ta esi tada ꞌatepatu, manuna tuta gete baleꞌuya tamiyami ꞌaboꞌada Keliso nadigega.  
\v 18 Ta ꞌida oboboma nina ꞌenega geyaꞌabo tamatamatauta, manuna oboboma ꞌaiꞌaila matauta ꞌiꞌewa yaulena. Onaꞌaiꞌaila, loina ꞌena tamatauta, ꞌeguma eobooboboma ꞌaiꞌaila nigeya ꞌedaya.   
\p
\v 19 \x * \xo 4:19 \xt 1 Yo 4:10\x*Ta ꞌida oboboma nina ꞌalena gete manuna Yaubada ꞌigimi obobomeda.   
\p
\v 20 ꞌEguma yaita ꞌigwae, “Yaubada yaobobomena,” ta ꞌabo tai nina tasina ꞌietalauwale, tauna tokabo, manuna tasidai taꞌitaꞌita, ꞌenega ꞌabo tasidai nigeya taoboobobome, nigeya sawesawedaya be Yaubada taobobome, tauna nigeya tada ꞌitena.   
\p
\v 21 \x * \xo 4:21 \xt Md 5:44-45; Mk 12:29-31\x*Ta ꞌada loina Yaubada ꞌenega be ꞌaene tauna taobobome, ta wate tasidao taobobomedi.   
\c 5  
\s1 Yesu ꞌana emisa ꞌiewaiwai bubuna baleꞌu ꞌenaya  
\p
\v 1 ꞌEguma maiboꞌada Yesu taemise ꞌaene tauna Toꞌetoseyana, ꞌaboꞌada Yaubada natunao. Ta wate ꞌeguma Tamana taobobome, natunao nadigega taobobomedi.  
\v 2 ꞌEnega ꞌeguma Yaubada taobobome, ta ꞌeguma ꞌina loinao taematamatanedi, tamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene Yaubada natunao wate taobobomedi.  
\v 3 \x * \xo 5:3 \xt Yo 14:15, 23-24; Md 11:30\x*Manuna Yaubada ꞌana oboboma be ꞌina loina ꞌana ematamatana leleleya, ta ꞌina loina nidi nigeya mwaudi, ta esi kapekapeyadi.  
\v 4 \x * \xo 5:4 \xt Yo 16:33\x*ꞌEnega ꞌeguma Yaubada ꞌienatuneda, bubuna baleꞌu taewaiwai sine, ta ꞌida ꞌebe ewaiwai nina ꞌana esana emisa.  
\v 5 \x * \xo 5:5 \xt Lo 8:37\x*Manuna ꞌabo Yesu taemise ꞌaene Yaubada Natuna, gete ꞌenega bubuna baleꞌu taewaiwai sine.   
\s1 Yaubada Natuna ꞌana simana manuna  
\p
\v 6 \x * \xo 5:6 \xt Yo 1:29-34\x*Ta Natuna ꞌina mai ꞌedaya nate bwasiyega ta wate lalanega, tauna Yesu Keliso, nigeya bwasi namo ꞌenega, ta esi bwasi be lala wate ꞌediyega. Gete manuna Yaubada Yaluyaluwana ꞌisimasimana ꞌaiꞌaila manuna Yaluyaluwana adelina palupaluna.  
\v 7 \x * \xo 5:7 \xt Yo 15:26\x*Manuna Yesu ꞌana tosimanao ꞌetoi simiyami,  
\v 8 nate Yaluyaluwa ta bwasi ta lala, ta ꞌidi eꞌita leleleya.   
\p
\v 9 \x * \xo 5:9 \xt Yo 5:32-37, 8:18\x*ꞌEguma tomota ꞌidi simanao taemisedi, sawesawenaya be Yaubada ꞌina simana taemise, manuna Yaubada tauna Toewaiwai, ga Natuna manuna ꞌisimana ꞌedaya.  
\v 10 \x * \xo 5:10 \xt Ga 4:6\x*ꞌEnega ꞌeguma tauna taemise, ꞌatedaya talotoo ꞌaene tauna Yaubada Natuna. Ta esi ꞌeguma Yaubada geyaꞌabo taemiemise, gote ꞌenega taꞌawa kabokaboe, manuna ꞌina simana Natuna manuna nigeya taemiemise.  
\v 11 Ta ꞌina simana nina ꞌaene Natunana ꞌenega yawasida ataya ꞌiꞌebwaꞌeda.  
\v 12 \x * \xo 5:12 \xt Yo 3:36\x*ꞌEnega ꞌabo yaita Yaubada Natuna ꞌenaya ꞌimiyami, tai nina yawasina boboꞌana niꞌatu ꞌilobena, ta ꞌabo yaita nigeya Yaubada Natuna ꞌenaya, tauna nigeya.   
\s1 Yawasi ataya manuna  
\p
\v 13 \x * \xo 5:13 \xt Yo 20:31\x*ꞌImi leta gete niꞌatu yaꞌetoladinawa be wamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene ꞌeguma Yaubada Natuna ꞌana esanega waemiemisa, yawasimi ataya waloba,  
\v 14 \x * \xo 5:14 \xt Yo 14:13\x*be wate matanaya ꞌada lotoona ꞌaene ꞌida sidasida ꞌinonodi, be ꞌiꞌebwaꞌeda toꞌase be toꞌase tasidasida manudi, ꞌabo tauna ꞌina nuwena wate nadigega.  
\v 15 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌida sidao maiboꞌadi ꞌinonodi, ꞌenega tamwalatonina ꞌaene ꞌida sidao nidi ꞌieꞌisedi.   
\p
\v 16 \x * \xo 5:16 \xt Md 12:31\x*ꞌAina loegesi ꞌadi eꞌisa mwawasa ta ꞌaidi nigeya, ꞌenega ꞌeguma yaita ꞌoyo tasiyo ꞌuꞌita ꞌiloegesi, ta loegesi nina gidalina ta nigeya ꞌana eꞌisa mwawasa, ꞌenega ꞌeguma toloegesi nina manuna ꞌusisida Yaubada ꞌenaya, Yaubada ꞌimu sida ꞌida nono, be tasiyo yawasina ꞌida tagwale. Ta esi loegesi nidi ꞌadi eꞌisa mwawasa, geyaꞌabo manudi wasidasida Yaubada ꞌenaya.  
\v 17 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, loegesi maiboꞌadi toꞌumalidi, ta ꞌaidi ꞌadi eꞌisa nigeya mwawasa.   
\p
\v 18 \x * \xo 5:18 \xt Yo 17:15\x*Ta esi tamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene ꞌabo Yaubada ꞌienatuneda geyaꞌabo taloeloegesi, manuna tauna Yaubada ꞌigimi enatunenaya ꞌiꞌitaꞌiꞌisida, be geyaꞌabo tauna totoꞌumalina nina ꞌigitogitooda.   
\p
\v 19 Ta wate ꞌaboꞌada tamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene Yaubada ꞌienatuneda, ta saꞌi baleꞌu bubunina ꞌana tomuliyao yauyaudi totoꞌumalina nina ꞌina bodao.   
\p
\v 20 \x * \xo 5:20 \xt Yo 17:3\x*Ta wate tamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene Yaubada Natuna niꞌatu ꞌimai ꞌedaya, ga ꞌigienuwa sabwalenida ꞌaene Yaubada Topalupaluna, ta ꞌenaya tamiyami, manuna ꞌaboꞌada Yaubada Natuna Yesu Keliso maꞌeda. Yesu nina Yaubada ꞌaiꞌaila, ta yawasida ataya ꞌalena.   
\p
\v 21 \x * \xo 5:21 \xt 1 Ko 10:14\x*Natugwao, wada ꞌitaꞌiꞌisimi mali ꞌebe emisao ꞌediyega, be wapilisinedi.   